  "_meta": {
    "doc": "CRAFTING / FORGE (consumes materials from loot). UPGRADE raises a gear instance's item-level (ilvl). RECIPES forge a fresh base gear piece from materials, but crafting is a SKILL: each recipe has a `discipline` (smithing/leatherwork/artificing/warding) and a `tier` (difficulty). Your per-discipline PROFICIENCY level (state.player.crafting[discipline]) sets the SUCCESS chance and the CRIT chance. A failed craft refunds part of the materials. A CRITICAL success yields a higher-tier item (`critUpgrade`) or, lacking one, a MASTERWORK (bonus ilvl). Crafting grants proficiency XP. Pure logic in src/systems/crafting.js. Materials from data/systems/loot.json.",
